OL,4,G1600FA New Life in the Sun
OL,5,     GIn France, new plans keep Andrew
OL,6,     Gand Richard on their toes. Best
OL,7,     Gfriends Janey and Sharon start an
OL,8,     Gadventure. And will the floor-
OL,9,     Gfillers fall flat at Abi and
OL,10,     GDarren's disco?
OL,11,G1700FFour in a Bed
OL,12,     GThe new run continues. The B&Bers
OL,13,     Gvisit Barbara and Elizabeth's
OL,14,     Gboutique B&B in Norfolk, where
OL,15,     Gthe hosts try to dance away some
OL,16,     Gdoubts about grout with an old-
OL,17,     Gschool Wurlitzer organ.
